File format
===========

We use the same levels of titles as the python documentation, namely ::

 ####
 Part
 ####

 *******
 Chapter
 *******

 Section
 =======

 Subsection
 ----------

 Subsubsection
 ^^^^^^^^^^^^^

 Paragraph
 """""""""

The figures will preferably be in SVG format, but this will likely be aligned once the first draft has been written. 

The links are defined in the top-level links.rst file which is importer in all restructured text files. 

